<InfoReplace>
	<DefaultInclude>false</DefaultInclude>

	<Description>Semi-auto D2

	Makes the D2 shotgun fire one round per trigger pull, thus being able to fire two round before requiring a reload.

	Changes made by this mod:
	[list]
	[*] The D2 fires one round per trigger pull. Two trigger pulls are required to empty the weapon.
	[*] The damage of each shot has been reduced by half, to account for only one shot being fired from the gun instead of two.
	[/list]

	Other Information:
	[list]
	[*] This mod is co-op friendly.
	[/list]

	Credits: 
	[list]
	[*] [size=1][color=lightgreen]Author: [/color][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/users/32262030][b]LinkHero95[/b][/url][/size]
	[/list]
	</Description>

	<Dependencies>
		<Dependency Name="Weapons" Action="or">
			<Package>BP Weapon Files.a3</Package>
		</Dependency>
	</Dependencies>

	<Category>3</Category>

	<Replaces>
